Name: end-of-stream
Description:
This Notify-Reason value indicates the end of a media
      stream.

Name: media-properties-update
Description:
This Notify-Reason value allows the server
      to indicate that the properties of the media has changed during
      the playout.

Name: scale-change
Description:
This Notify-Reason value allows the server to notify
      the client about a change in the Scale of the media.

Name: ice-restart
Description:
Server notifying the client about the need for an ICE
      restart. See Section 4.6 of [RFC-ietf-mmusic-rtsp-nat-22].
